title: 18 in. Ergonomic Mountain Mover Snow Shovel
description: This True Temper 18 in. Ergonomic Mountain Mover Snow Shovel is ideal for shoveling or pushing snow. The blade shape features a flat front end for pushing snow and slush while the deep back end is shaped to scoop snow. The nylon wear strip extends the life of the blade and prevents the gouging of decks and other surfaces. It also features an ergonomic handle and an oversized D-grip that easily accommodates a gloved hand.
